reviewText: Great game . Could not get any better other than to be a game called by Bear.  You have Bill Oliver calling the D that confused Miami so bad that Geno could not do anything.  Great game from a great coach Gene Stallings. To top it all off calling the came for the fans could only of been better if Eli Gold were calling it, but this man was a great friend of Bear's. Keith Jackson's voice is legend in college football and always will be just like Howard  Cosell. You need only hear a second of his voice to know him and know you were in for a treat.
Fun to watch such a classic game!
Roll Tide! This one brought the Tide back to national prominence after several unbalanced seasons. If you love the Tide or just great football, check this out!
Excellent quality. I was pleasantly surprised at the sharpness of the picture. Highly recommended.
not a good quality recording, too fuzzy and blurry
